Q.1 Gym Membership. If 0 month print invalid input and if 1 month then print 2000 and for 3 print 5000 and for 5 print 9000 and finally for 7 print 15000 rupees.

import java.util.*;
class Main {
public static void main(String[]args){
Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
